data.text: @InStyle Happy Birthday Meghan! 🎂🎉 She looks very nice at the Prince Harry's friend wedding! ☺️ I like her shoes! #MeghanMarkle #DuchessOfSussex
@InStyle This is my least favorite look on Meghan, but love her hat & shoes! She still looks flawless even in that dress!

@InStyle Shocking. Appearing in public barelegged w/o nylons? Zounds! Total breach of Royal Protocol. The Queen will not be pleased, eh wot. Americans, always wanting to break traditions. Ghastly, I say, ghastly.
@InStyle That dress is caput.  I like the shoes.
@InStyle Such strange clothes she wears in the summer.  Very dowdy.
